uture-for-israel-and-gaza/0000018c-b63e-db94-afbd-b67f74040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高中校长因在脸书上发帖同情加沙苦难而面临停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-high-school-principal-faces-suspension-for-sympathizing-with-suffering-of-gazans/0000018c-b09c-db94-afbd-b0fd76a80000</link><description>校长因在 Facebook 页面上发表《国土报》的文章而被传唤参加听证会，该文章批评以色列媒体对加沙人道主义危机缺乏报道</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 16:43:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-high-school-principal-faces-suspension-for-sympathizing-with-suffering-of-gazans/0000018c-b09c-db94-afbd-b0fd76a80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部城市罗德 10 岁和 20 岁少年遭枪击身亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article/.premium/10-year-old-20-year-old-fatally-shot-in-central-israeli-city-of-lod/0000018c-b65d-d45c-a98e-bf5d04280000</link><description>另一人是一名 28 岁男子，因枪击受了中度伤。周四，一名 35 岁男子在同城街道上刺伤一名两岁男孩后被捕</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 16:28:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article/.premium/10-year-old-20-year-old-fatally-shot-in-central-israeli-city-of-lod/0000018c-b65d-d45c-a98e-bf5d04280000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队任命周五在加沙北部战斗中丧生的以色列国防军预备役军官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article/israeli-army-names-idf-reserve-officer-killed-in-north-gaza-fighting-on-friday/0000018c-b652-d45c-a98e-bf5e7c260000</link><description>另据报道，另外两名以色列国防军士兵在加沙地带的多场战斗中受重伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 16:14:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-29/ty-article/israeli-army-names-idf-reserve-officer-killed-in-north-gaza-fighting-on-friday/0000018c-b652-d45c-a98e-bf5e7c260000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列领先的喜剧节目要追随 BBC、联合国和哈马斯的同情者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2023-12-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/veteran-israeli-comedy-show-goes-after-u-s-progressives-the-bbc-and-hamas-sympathizers/0000018c-b543-d014-a3cd-bf5f7dda0000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，热门电视节目“Eretz Nehederet”在一系列批判性短剧中代表了以色列的观点和愤怒，其中对西方媒体的“偏见”和自由派哈马斯辩护者等话题进行了讽刺。剧集主管穆里·塞格夫 (Muli Segev) 解释了他如何将其视为自己的战时任务，以及为什么《周六夜现场》大学校长短剧毫无意义</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Dec 2023 15:42:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/television/2023-12-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/veteran-israeli-comedy-show-goes-after-u-s-progressives-the-bbc-and-hamas-sympathizers/0000018c-b543-d014-a3cd-bf5f7dda0000</guid></item></channel></rss>